# Doow Website Rebuild

Use `AGENTS.md` and `docs/rebuild/` as the source of truth.

## Rules

- Work one batch at a time.
- Work one section at a time.
- Stop after each batch or section for review.
- Build mobile-first.
- Use Figma as the design source of truth.
- Use shared tokens and primitives before section-level UI.
- Avoid legacy assets and legacy marketing structure unless explicitly retained.

## Current public route policy

- Keep `/`, `/signin`, `/privacy_policy`, `/terms_of_use`
- Prune `/about_us` and `/contact_us` with redirects
